            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Absolute yields of the reactions C-12(g,n)C-11 and",
                " O-16(g,n)O-15 have been determined at 22-MeV end-point",
                " energy of the bremsstrahlung beam.",
                "for the reaction C-12(g,n)C-11 a yield curve from",
                " threshold to 24 MeV has been obtained and the cross-",
                " section curve for the reaction computed. A thorough",
                " comparison with other results has been made."
              ]
